        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Attius <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibertus</ex></expan> F<supplied reason="lost">a</supplied>ustus <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ivus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ecit</ex></expan> sibi et Attiae <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibertae</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Secundae coniugi <expan><abbr>sanc</abbr><ex>tissimae</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>et <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> Attio <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> Crispo <lb n="5"/>et <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> Attio <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> Secundo <lb n="6"/>coniugis amissae lacrumas satis esse putavi <lb n="7"/>me fudisse meae vimque tulisse deum <lb n="8"/>et tuleram graviter sed nunc et <expan><abbr>sol</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> et orbus <lb n="9"/>amissis natis maxima damna fleo <lb n="10"/>et testor superos p<supplied reason="lost">at</supplied>ri qu<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> ponere nati <lb n="11"/>debuerant natis ponere dona patrem </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Attia <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>iberta</ex></expan> Ampliata <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> XXIII <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ita</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>florente aetate depressere veneficiae <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>mensesq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>quinq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> et annum cum aegrotaverit <lb n="5"/>abreptam aetate in inferi Ditis specus <lb n="6"/>hunc titulum posuit Faustus libertae suae
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Drei aneinander passende Fragmente bekannt. Ein Fragment ist verschollen, zwei Fragmente befinden sich in den Museen von Split und Trogir. Abmessungen des größten Fragments: s. o.; Abmessungen der beiden übrigen Fragmente: 74 x 52, 63 x 38 x 28.</p>
